At long last, Beyonc√© finally won album of the year at the Grammys when her Billboard 200-topping album Cowboy Carter took home album of the year. It was one of the biggest moments in the making in Recording Academy history, as the superstar‚Äôs lack of recognition in the major categories continued even as she became the institution‚Äôs winningest artist of all time in 2023.

But while the AOTY win was certainly Bey‚Äôs biggest feat of the night, her shocked reaction to hearing her name read off as the winner of best country album ended up being the most viral moment ‚Äî one that remains a frequently used meme online as 2025 draws to a close.

