The phrase immediately became a staple in the 2025 lexicon, with the singer‚Äôs wife, Rhode founder Hailey Bieber, writing on Instagram Stories after the release of Justin‚Äôs Daisies album, ‚ÄúIs it finally clocking to you f‚Äìking losers?‚Äù

