After years of writing love songs, Taylor Swift finally got her own happy ending when Travis Kelce proposed to her in August. ‚ÄúYour English teacher and gym teacher are getting married,‚Äù the couple wrote on Instagram while announcing the news, leaving Swifties everywhere overjoyed.

As we learned later, the Kansas City Chiefs tight end popped the question right after he and Swift recorded their record-breaking New Heights podcast episode, during which the pop star had no idea a team of people was setting up their rose garden proposal backdrop right outside their house while she was discussing her The Life of a Showgirl album on the show.

